snippet.title: FashionVerse | Official Game Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
From café chic to red-carpet glam, dress clients for all occasions. Flaunt your fashion sense in daily challenges and vote on the community’s top looks.

Play FashionVerse on your mobile devices. Available exclusively on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/game/81715811

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services with over 247 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.
